1. Convert OTF/TTF into BDF
otf2bdf font.ttf -p size -o font.bdf

2. Edit AVERAGE_WIDTH to an even number in the generated BDF file

3. Convert BDF to PSF
bdf2psf --fb font.bdf /usr/share/bdf2psf/standard.equivalents /usr/share/bdf2psf/fontsets/Uni2.512 512 font.psf

3. Convert PSF to C include file
psf2inc font.psf font.c